类 RenderHighlightEvent.Entity

java.lang.Object

net.minecraftforge.client.event.RenderHighlightEvent.Entity
封闭类:
RenderHighlightEvent
public static class RenderHighlightEvent.Entity extends RenderHighlightEvent
Fired before an entity's selection highlight is rendered.

This event is not cancellable, and does not have a result.

This event is fired on the main Forge event bus, only on the logical client.
